phole extends to freshly-sown grass seed as well (in Thames Water’s case, if it was sown by a business as a service).\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e‘You can water your grass seed for the first 28 days with a hosepipe,’ says Yorkshire Water. ‘After that, you’ll need to use a watering can. Please use the hosepipe sparingly and try to use it for a short amount of time.’\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure data-bordeaux-image-check=\"\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/DeAMUTi6rxnpsQ674AkBZo-1920-80.jpg.webp 1920w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/DeAMUTi6rxnpsQ674AkBZo-1600-80.jpg.webp 1600w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/DeAMUTi6rxnpsQ674AkBZo-1280-80.jpg.webp 1280w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/DeAMUTi6rxnpsQ674AkBZo-1024-80.jpg.webp 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/DeAMUTi6rxnpsQ674AkBZo-768-80.jpg.webp 768w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/DeAMUTi6rxnpsQ674AkBZo-415-80.jpg.webp 415w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/DeAMUTi6rxnpsQ674AkBZo-360-80.jpg.webp 360w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/DeAMUTi6rxnpsQ674AkBZo-320-80.jpg.webp 320w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 710px) 670px, calc(100vw - 30px)\"/\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/DeAMUTi6rxnpsQ674AkBZo.jpg\" alt=\"Planted border surrounding grass lawn in garden\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/DeAMUTi6rxnpsQ674AkBZo-1920-80.jpg 1920w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/DeAMUTi6rxnpsQ674AkBZo-1600-80.jpg 1600w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/DeAMUTi6rxnpsQ674AkBZo-1280-80.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/DeAMUTi6rxnpsQ674AkBZo-1024-80.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/DeAMUTi6rxnpsQ674AkBZo-768-80.jpg 768w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/DeAMUTi6rxnpsQ674AkBZo-415-80.jpg 415w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/DeAMUTi6rxnpsQ674AkBZo-360-80.jpg 360w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/DeAMUTi6rxnpsQ674AkBZo-320-80.jpg 320w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 710px) 670px, ca